            <abstract>
                <p>This keyword is used to classify additiones.</p>
                <p>Despite the wide-spread opinion that qǝne is a poetic improvisation which is not written down, a number of manuscripts contain qǝne-poems, for example as additional notes. 
                    Frequently it is clearly stated the poem is qǝne, and even the type is indicated.</p>
